1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:01,553
Waldensop: Good morn, lady.

2
00:00:01,607 --> 00:00:04,346
A noble person such as yourself on foot, then?

3
00:00:04,466 --> 00:00:05,893
If it's rest you seek,

4
00:00:05,918 --> 00:00:08,380
you'll get precious little comfort in this thieves' den,

5
00:00:08,405 --> 00:00:09,540
I'll tell you.

6
00:00:09,927 --> 00:00:12,019
Be careful if you go inside, milady!

7
00:00:12,147 --> 00:00:14,340
Some people in these parts would rob you

8
00:00:14,365 --> 00:00:16,407
same as look at you, they would.

